, he would find it is better for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23916,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/26\/fudayl-forgive-defeat-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":23928,"position":1},"title":"Fudayl on Mercy: Whoever forgives others has defeated Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 26, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Razin reported: A man came to Al-Fudayl ibn Bazwan, may Allah have mercy on him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, a man has slandered you!\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cVerily, I will infuriate the one who commanded him! May Allah forgive me and forgive him.\u201d It was said, \u201cWho has commanded him?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24323,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/01\/ibn-al-mubarak-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":23928,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mubarak on Ikhlaas: Best deed is to be sincere to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Dunya reported: Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked, \u201cWhich deed is best?\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cSincerity to Allah.\u201d Source: al-Amr bil-Ma\u2019ru\u0304f li Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 71 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0646\u064a\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0